HEADWORD: Bondslave
<hw>Bond"slave`</hw> <pr>(-sl⟦amac⟧v`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A person
in a state of slavery; one whose person and liberty are subjected to the
authority of a master.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

